Percona Server for MongoDB is a free, enhanced, fully compatible, open source, drop-in replacement for the MongoDB Community Edition that includes enterprise-grade features and functionality.

Percona Server for MongoDB provides:

* All features and benefits of MongoDB 3.2 Community Edition.
* MongoDB distributed MMAP v1 and WiredTiger storage engines
* Optional RocksDB and Percona Memory Engine storage engines
* Full online backup support for PerconaFT and MongoRocks
* SASL Authentication plugin, enabling authentication through OpenLDAP or Active Directory.
* Audit plugin, providing the ability to track and query database interactions of users or applications
